00:17:09,863 --> 00:17:11,863
First of all, our family needed someone...

498
00:17:11,863 --> 00:17:14,733
to run this business properly.

499
00:17:14,733 --> 00:17:18,563
Secondly, I'm a mother.

500
00:17:18,563 --> 00:17:20,133
Back then, I had to go on so many business trips.

501
00:17:20,133 --> 00:17:21,673
I also had to work late often.

502
00:17:21,673 --> 00:17:24,773
I rarely got to spend time with my children.

503
00:17:24,773 --> 00:17:26,513
So when my mother asked us...

504
00:17:26,513 --> 00:17:29,583
if we were interested in running the sauna,

505
00:17:29,883 --> 00:17:33,183
I thought I would be able to work and look after my children.

506
00:17:33,183 --> 00:17:35,153
That crossed my mind.

507
00:17:35,153 --> 00:17:37,783
- So you decided to run it? - Yes, I told her I'd do it.

508
00:17:38,583 --> 00:17:40,493
- I decided to join her. - Together.

509
00:17:40,493 --> 00:17:41,693
I see.

510
00:17:41,993 --> 00:17:44,723
I understand that you guys are sisters and all.

511
00:17:44,723 --> 00:17:47,833
But running a business with your family members can't be easy.

512
00:17:47,833 --> 00:17:50,733
- Running a business together... - It's not easy.

513
00:17:50,733 --> 00:17:53,233
- You might have different opinions. - We fought yesterday too.

514
00:17:53,773 --> 00:17:55,373
If you don't mind me asking, could you tell us...

515
00:17:55,373 --> 00:17:57,243
what the disagreement was about?

516
00:17:57,243 --> 00:17:58,643
When we work together, we say things like,

517
00:17:58,973 --> 00:18:01,213
"We should do it like this." "No, it should be done like this."

518
00:18:01,213 --> 00:18:03,183
"Why didn't you prepare that?"

519
00:18:03,183 --> 00:18:06,683
But more importantly, our MBTI is completely different.

520
00:18:06,683 --> 00:18:08,453
- What are your MBTI types? - What are your MBTI types?

521
00:18:08,983 --> 00:18:10,353
I'm an ESTJ.

522
00:18:10,623 --> 00:18:11,983
I'm an INFP.

523
00:18:11,983 --> 00:18:14,723
(They are total opposites.)

524
00:18:14,953 --> 00:18:16,393
- You're total opposites. - You're completely different.

525
00:18:16,823 --> 00:18:18,293
I'm an ISFP.

526
00:18:18,293 --> 00:18:20,493
I see. I feel like we belong in the same club.

527
00:18:20,493 --> 00:18:21,933
You don't like complicating things, right?

528
00:18:21,933 --> 00:18:23,133
- I don't. - Right.

529
00:18:23,133 --> 00:18:26,133
I just don't do anything. I do all my tasks at once.

530
00:18:26,133 --> 00:18:27,273
Do you prefer hotels to camping?

531
00:18:27,273 --> 00:18:28,673
I prefer hotels to camping.

532
00:18:29,173 --> 00:18:30,643
I know what you mean.

533
00:18:30,703 --> 00:18:33,273
As a planner, you must prepare things months in advance.

534
00:18:33,273 --> 00:18:36,143
"Did you do it?" "Will you do it?" I keep asking her.

535
00:18:36,143 --> 00:18:37,213
- "I'll do it." - Then...

536
00:18:37,683 --> 00:18:38,683
- Right. - she says she'll do it.

537
00:18:38,683 --> 00:18:40,683
- "I'll do it." - "I'm going to do it."

538
00:18:40,683 --> 00:18:42,253
"I'll do it at my own pace."

539
00:18:42,413 --> 00:18:43,823
- "I'll take care of it." - "Don't worry. I'll do it."

540
00:18:43,823 --> 00:18:46,023
"Why do you keep rushing me?"

541
