- Right. "Why won't she do it?" - "No."

542
00:18:47,993 --> 00:18:50,093
- "I just have to finish by then." - Right.

543
00:18:50,093 --> 00:18:52,463
- That's all. Right. - It's okay as long as it's done.

544
00:18:53,433 --> 00:18:54,793
(Annoyed)

545
00:18:55,933 --> 00:18:58,433
- She's frustrated. - Yes. Totally.

546
00:18:58,633 --> 00:19:00,373
That's understandable.

547
00:19:01,573 --> 00:19:03,073
When we work together,

548
00:19:03,073 --> 00:19:04,803
our different personality helps a lot.

549
00:19:04,803 --> 00:19:06,573
- Right. - We're very different.

550
00:19:06,573 --> 00:19:08,873
When we have to make important decisions,

551
00:19:08,873 --> 00:19:10,783
we're able to include different opinions.

552
00:19:10,783 --> 00:19:13,153
That way, we can look at it from all angles.

553
00:19:13,153 --> 00:19:14,583
- We're helpful to each other. - I see.

554
00:19:15,383 --> 00:19:17,253
