556
00:19:19,023 --> 00:19:20,123
from elementary through high school.

557
00:19:20,123 --> 00:19:22,793
We even had the same major in college.

558
00:19:22,793 --> 00:19:25,023
- Really? - Yes. We had the same major.

559
00:19:25,023 --> 00:19:26,063
We majored in the same field.

560
00:19:26,063 --> 00:19:28,063
