567
00:19:38,043 --> 00:19:41,213
How is it like having your sister constantly in your life?

568
00:19:41,613 --> 00:19:42,983
- We know everything. - Right.

569
00:19:42,983 --> 00:19:44,843
We know each other's friends...

570
00:19:44,843 --> 00:19:47,083
- and schoolteachers. - Really?

571
00:19:47,383 --> 00:19:48,913
You must know everything...

572
00:19:48,913 --> 00:19:50,453
