573
00:19:50,453 --> 00:19:51,453
- Right. - Seriously.

574
00:19:51,623 --> 00:19:52,853
- You guys are the best partners. - Yes.

575
00:19:54,723 --> 00:19:56,563
But it's not like we can't live without one another.

576
00:19:56,563 --> 00:19:58,793
- We're not that affectionate. - We're not.

577
00:19:59,123 --> 00:20:00,833
