00:22:08,423 --> 00:22:10,223
- Gosh, this is... - This is hard.

639
00:22:10,463 --> 00:22:12,563
- This is really hard. - It's not easy.

640
00:22:12,923 --> 00:22:14,363
- How about doing it like this? - This is allowed, right?

641
